data.description: A rare opportunity exists to own this custom single level home sitting on 2.24 acres of flat usable land. The potential for this expansive gated property is limitless, offering a plethora of income-generating possibilities. From constructing a personalized ADU to providing RV parking and storage facilities, to transforming it into a prime horse property, the options are endless. The lot featrues 3 RV cleanouts, electrical power in rear lot, 6 water spigets, 4 gates to access the rear of the lot, a green house, 2 sheds & private gated entry. Upon stepping into the foyer, one immediately recognizes the presence of 10-foot ceilings that extend seamlessly throughout the entire home. You are greeted by open & bright formal living & dining spaces. The home opens into a spacious area seamlessly integrating the kitchen, family room, and casual dining space that brings a sense of space & comfort to this home. The kitchen features granite counter tops, custom cabinetry, walk in pantry, a kitchen island with utility sink and an oversized counter for convienant bar stool seating. The family room is spacious featuring a fireplace & mountain views. The home offers 4 spacious bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms & 1 guest bathroom. The spacious primary suite features a dual fireplace, 2 large walk in closets, a glass slider door leading to the backyard and a private retreat. Primary bathroom features dual separated sinks, jetted jacuzzi tub and a huge custom walk in shower equipped with dual shower heads. One of the bedrooms boasts an en suite full bathroom. Two of the bedrooms feature a Jack n Jill bathroom. All bedrooms include ceiling fans. Custom windows throughout the home. The backyard is an intrinsic part of the overall design of this home featuring an extended covered patio, a 40X50 patio slab with gazebo & enjoy the mountain views! The lot includes fruit trees, palm trees & a greenhouse. This custom home also features a oversized 3 car garage. This home is a MUST SEE with endless possibilites! Kindly remember to explore the 3D virtual tour link, which includes the floorplan of the home as well.
